<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <title>Query Page</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>
          a) List country and city names whose PM 2.5 values are greater than 50
          in 2015.
        </h2>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <form action="/query/1" method="post">
            <label for="formFile" class="form-label"
              >query and download excel file</label
            >
            <br />
            <input
              type="submit"
              class="btn btn-primary mt-1"
              value="Query and Download"
            />
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr />
      <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>
          b) Calculate the AVG(PM 2.5) by country (show the results in a
          decreasing order).
        </h2>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <form action="/query/2" method="post">
            <label for="formFile" class="form-label"
              >query and download excel file</label
            >
            <br />
            <input
              type="submit"
              class="btn btn-primary mt-1"
              value="Query and Download"
            />
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr />

      <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>
          c) Given a <-country_input-> from the user, show a historical PM 2.5
          values by year.
        </h2>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <form action="/query/3" method="post">
            <label class="form-label">query and download excel file</label>
            <br />
            <label for="country_input" class="form-label">country_input</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control"
              id="country_input"
              name="country_input"
              placeholder="country_input"
            />
            <br />
            <input
              type="submit"
              class="btn btn-primary mt-1"
              value="Query and Download"
            />
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr />

      <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>
            d) Given a <-year_input-> and an input of <-color_pm25-> level of health concern
                from the user, calculate a total of the affected population (in number).
        </h2>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <form action="/query/4" method="post">
            <label class="form-label"
              >query and download excel file</label
            >
            <br />
            <label for="year_input" class="form-label">year_input</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control"
              id="year_input"
              name="year_input"
              placeholder="year_input"
            />
            <label for="color_pm25" class="form-label">color_pm25</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control"
              id="color_pm25"
              name="color_pm25"
              placeholder="color_pm25"
            />
            <br />
            <input
              type="submit"
              class="btn btn-primary mt-1"
              value="Query and Download"
            />
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr />


    </div>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
